rows.label: qst105406_msg0002
rows.name:
You have collected all the
treasures. It must have
been quite an ordeal.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0003
rows.name: Heh... It was alright, I guess.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0004
rows.name:
Rex... I bestow upon you the
title of King of Salvagers.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0006
rows.name:
Ah, my apologies... Perhaps
that is an old-fashioned title
for a young man of today.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0007
rows.name: No! It's cool! King of Salvagers!

rows.label: qst105406_msg0008
rows.name:
I'm the King... the
salvager of salvagers.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0010
rows.name:
It is I who should be thanking you. I
am sorry for making you deal with
something I left behind in my youth.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0011
rows.name:
It is not just the title.
I would like you to accept
my thanks as well.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0101
rows.name:
It seems you have gathered them...
Could you let me speak with Rex?
